# oracledb-monitor — Git Workflow (Mandatory)

Applies to **all Git operations** (pull, branch, commit, push, MR) in this repo.

**Source of truth**: `.cursor/CONVENTIONS.md` · `.cursor/project.manifest.json` → `git`

> `canalframe-git-workflow.mdc` 축약 이식판 — 단일 레포라 멀티레포 반복 절차는 제외.

## 1. Work start (before edit / commit / MR)

1. `git fetch origin`
2. `git checkout main` (또는 manifest `git.baseBranch`)
3. `git pull origin main`
4. `git checkout -b feature/<short-slug>` (prefix from manifest `git.featureBranchPrefix`)
5. **Do not** commit directly on `main` unless owner explicitly requests hotfix

Coordinator (**@co**) and implementing teams run steps 1–4 **before** first code change when the session involves Git.

## 2. Commit message format

```
[{author}] {summary}
```

- `{author}`: manifest `git.authorName` → else `git config user.name` → else ask owner once per session
- Use **`git commit -m "…"` only** — no `--trailer`

**Example**: `[이종필] 슬로우쿼리 추이 그래프 추가`

## 3. Merge Request (MR)

- **Target branch**: `main` (manifest `git.mrTargetBranch`)
- Push feature branch, open MR **into `main`**
- Push / MR creation **only on explicit owner request**

## 4. Role ownership

| Action | Owner |
|--------|--------|
| Pull + feature branch at session start | **@co** (Coordinator) |
| Commit with format above | Implementing team + **@co** on owner commit request |
| MR draft / publish | **@co** |
